    <item>
      <title>Bridge for iOS and Android</title>
      <link>http://www.ivanferdelja.com/project/bridge/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Sep 2016 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://www.ivanferdelja.com/project/bridge/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href =&#34;http://www.trybridge.com&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Bridge &lt;/a&gt;is a need-based search, communication, and networking tool that helps you find and access the right person for whatever you need, leveraging the network effect (“six degrees of separation”) of your friends and colleagues.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Bridge is also an omnipresent social capital exchange / platform / wallet, keeping track of &amp;ldquo;favors” between people, estimating how close the a person is to everyone in his or her network (phonebook) and establishing virtual currency that represents the &amp;ldquo;social capital&amp;rdquo; of each user.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;App is currently in private beta.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a target=&#34;_blank&#34; href=&#39;http://www.trybridge.com&#39;&gt;
&lt;figure class=&#34;post-image&#34;&gt;
    
        &lt;img src=&#34;http://www.ivanferdelja.com/img/bridge.png&#34; /&gt;
    
    
&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>AgentCASH Smart POS for Android</title>
      <link>http://www.ivanferdelja.com/project/agent-cash/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Nov 2015 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://www.ivanferdelja.com/project/agent-cash/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href =&#34;http://www.agentcash.com&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;AgentCASH &lt;/a&gt; is a mobile payment system for Android that allows businesses to accept card or cash payments any place, any time.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;App fully supports all requirements of a small or medium business.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Some of the features:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;add, edit and organise all products or services into a neat, clean and visually informative page system&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;run cash or card payments (via a Bluetooth card reader)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;print receipts or issue them by e-mail and text messages&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;manage customers and invoices&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;playstore-link&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; href=&#39;https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.agentcash.register&amp;hl=en&amp;utm_source=global_co&amp;utm_medium=prtnr&amp;utm_content=Mar2515&amp;utm_campaign=PartBadge&amp;pcampaignid=MKT-Other-global-all-co-prtnr-py-PartBadge-Mar2515-1&#39;&gt;&lt;img alt=&#39;Get it on Google Play&#39; src=&#39;https://play.google.com/intl/en_us/badges/images/generic/en_badge_web_generic.png&#39;/&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

