      <description>&lt;p&gt;Colored Tabs is a concept Android app to explore aspects of &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.google.com/design/spec/material-design/introduction.html&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Material design&lt;/a&gt; such as immersion, cards etc.&lt;/p&gt;

